<span class="thumb"><img src="https://rpr.c.yimg.jp/im_siggh9C5okwfzI6lfRzqsyq3Ig---x64-y64/yn/rpr/matsumotohirofumi/profile-1501736365.jpeg" width="32" height="32" alt=""></span>
<span class="name">松本博文</span><span class="title">&nbsp;|&nbsp;将棋ライター </span>
